            today. Challenges such as climate change, human nutrition, comp=
etition=20
            between food and non-food crops, the exhaustion of fossil resou=
rces=20
            and appropriate land management put agronomists in a position t=
o generate=20
            compatible economic, social and environmental development.<br>
