            &gt;&gt;&gt; About Fluidigm<br>
            Fluidigm develops, manufactures and markets proprietary Integra=
ted=20
            Fluidic Circuit (IFC) systems that significantly improve produc=
tivity=20
            in life science research. Fluidigm=92s IFCs enable the simultan=
eous=20
            performance of thousands of sophisticated biochemical measureme=
nts=20
            in extremely minute volumes. These =93integrated circuits for b=
iology=94=20
            are made possible by miniaturizing and integrating liquid handl=
ing=20
            components on a single microfluidic device. Fluidigm=92s system=
